Project folder needs to be inside 'htdocs' folder in Xampp.
In PhpMyAdmin make database called 'test' and import 'test.sql' file which is included in folder.
Main routes are index.php?page=products and index.php?page=login.
All folders are protected with .htaccess file.
Admin user credentials are email pera@gmail.com, and password pera123.
Regular user credentials are email mika@gmail.com, and password mika123.
Products are listed in 3x3 grid.
Comments are listed down below. Non-users and regular users can see public comments.
Admin can see all comments and decide which one to make public or private or delete.
Form for creating comments is below listed comments.
